# Use Bun (not npm/npx)

This repo uses **Bun** as its package manager (`packageManager: bun@…` in `package.json`; `bun.lock` only).

## Commands

| Do | Not |
|----|-----|
| `bun install` | `npm install`, `npm ci` |
| `bun run dev`, `bun run test`, `bun run typecheck` | `npm run …` |
| `bunx shadcn@latest add …` | `npx shadcn@latest …` |
| `bunx convex dev` | `npx convex dev` |
| `bunx convex deploy` | `npx convex deploy` |
| `bunx convex env set KEY value` | `npx convex env set …` |
| `bunx convex run …` | `npx convex run …` |
| `bunx convex ai-files install` | `npx convex ai-files install` |

## Convex

- **Development:** `bunx convex dev` — watches and syncs to the dev deployment.
- **Production:** `bunx convex deploy` — deploy backend only; never use during local dev.

Do not add `package-lock.json`.
